USE OF THYROID HORMONE CONVERSION INHIBITORS - The present invention is directed to the use of thyroid hormone conversion inhibitors to treat hyperproliferative skin disorders, preferably their use in topical admixtures.

Compositions for Providing Vitamin D Year Round and Uses Thereof - Methods for enhancing the ability of an individual, exposed to sunlight, to produce vitamin D via the skin.
